review_3_text:
this is a franchise in a fairly large chain;
this one is in an excellent location; little competition;
tiny place;
i was staying nearby and visited early in the morning, door was open, no-one around except girl behind counter; she said 'we are not open', then pointed to her watch; 7:22; opens at 7:30;
no others customers waiting; wouldnt serve me;
if they were smart they would lock the front door until they were open
or she could have pointed to one of the few inside tables and said 'please wait there for just a small while';
but no , rather gruffly 'we are NOT open';
o well, we reached an agreement then and there , i agreed to never again try to be a customer there and quite possibly at any other chain location and she agreed not to serve me or be polite about it
